      "content": "it just feels so heavy. like i'm dragging this weight around every single day for no reason. everyone keeps telling me \"it'll get better\" or \"time heals,\" but they don't get it. it doesn't feel like healing, it just feels like i'm waiting for a clock to stop ticking. how am i supposed to keep doing this when the person who made everything make sense is just... gone? it feels like i'm just a ghost living a life that doesn't belong to me anymore.",
